{
  "category": "binding",
  "title": "Binding attributes",
  "description": {
    "en": "Binding attributes link JSON values to ViewModel state via the `@{...}` syntax. Three kinds: value binding, string resolution, and event binding.",
    "ja": "Binding 属性は `@{...}` 構文で JSON 値と ViewModel の状態を繋ぐ。値 binding、文字列解決、イベント binding の 3 種類がある。"
  },
  "kicker": "Attribute category · Reference",
  "kickerParentLabel": "Attributes",
